OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Ffrequent showers, some heavy and
OL,7,Fmerging into longer spells of rain,
OL,8,Fespecially over Shetland. Drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter spells for Orkney. Strong
OL,10,Fnortherly winds, which may reach gale
OL,11,Fforce in the morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy for Shetland with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of showery rain throughout.
OL,15,FMostly cloudy for Orkney with a few
OL,16,Fshowers and some clearer intervals.
OL,17,FStrong northerly winds easing
OL,18,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
