OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FFor Orkney, a largely dry
OL,6,Fday with sunny spells and just the odd
OL,7,Fshower possible. Cloudy for Shetland
OL,8,Fwith outbreaks of rain continuing
OL,9,Fthrough the day. Moderate
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fon Sunday with rain spreading and
OL,14,Fclearing northeastwards. A few showers
OL,15,FMonday but generally drier with sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Cloudy with rain Tuesday.
OL,17,FModerate winds becoming strong on
OL,18,FTuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
